我只能说貌似安装各种东西都有那么一句黄金命令行
对于安装homebrew,也基本上只需要这么一句
/usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"
可以稍微看一下

adong6666deiMac:~ adong666666$ /usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"
==> This script will install:
/usr/local/bin/brew
